text: Jasmina Novokmet (born 8 September 1969 in Pristina, Yugoslavia) is a Serbian conductor, professor of conducting and former associate dean at the Faculty of Arts of Priština. She is a former student of Jovan Šajnović. Category:Living people Category:1969 births Category:Serbian musicians Category:Conductors Category:People from Pristina
title: Jasmina Novokmet
